== ICC Profiles in X Specification ==
The specification describes ICC profile attchment to monitor hardware inside X to achieve network transparency.

=== Mailinglist ===
The spec was proposed and maintained over the OpenIcc [[http://lists.freedesktop.org/mailman/listinfo/openicc|email list]].

